    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub is aswritten's narrative spine: mission, positioning, founder backstory, and the product thesis of narrative steering. The core positioning moved on a dated arc — [\"install expertise into your AI\"](narr:Claim_CoreValuePropInstallExpertise) crystallized Mar 19, the [finalized tagline](narr:Claim_TaglineFinalized) landed the same day, Scarlet [dropped the \"memory\" word for \"installable expertise\"](narr:Obs_ScarletInstallableExpertise) Mar 23, then a May 18 [reframe to agent-deployment ROI](narr:Claim_PitchReframeAgentDeployment). The underlying thesis runs deeper: [steering as worldview bootloading](narr:Observation_1), [narrative as a vector in embedding space](narr:Narrative_NarrativeAsVector), and a unifying May 26 frame that [each use case is a steering loop plus a memory substrate](narr:Narrative_SteeringLoopPlusMemorySubstrate). Bridging metaphors recur — [AI as a new hire](narr:Narrative_AIAsNewHireBridgingInsight), the [optometrist model](narr:Observation_OptometristMetaphor), founder lessons from [Elephant Collective](narr:Narrative_ElephantCollective) and [Vouch's manual SSoT](narr:Observation_VouchSSoT). The [personal why](narr:Narrative_PersonalWhyAlternativeHealthcare) — alternative-healthcare navigation — anchors values. Style observations and brand stylization sit alongside as voice/witness material.""" ;
